messages.title: A Fresh Start with Lib Dem Jo Shaw
messages.content: Jo is fighting for our local services - like the Whittington Hospital A&E

messages.title: Only Jo Shaw can give us the fresh start that Camden needs
messages.content: Jo will be a different kind of MP for Camden.

keyPolicies.policyDescription: Jo is campaigning for fairer taxes.
Jo is campaigning with local residents against Labour cuts to our NHS. Her campaign to save the Whittington Hospital A&E has won respect from local people.
Jo especially calls in Camden to cut class sizes to 15 for our youngest children.
Jo Shaw is fighting for an extra 3,000 police to patrol our streets.

issues.education: Jo especially calls in Camden to cut class sizes to 15 for our youngest children.
issues.health: Jo is campaigning with local residents against Labour cuts to our NHS. Her campaign to save the Whittington Hospital A&E has won respect from local people.

leaflet.personalStatement: Jo Shaw - a different kind of MP. Jo is a tireless campaigner for our NHS. She’s fighting for our hard-hit borough and will be the campaigning MP that local people deserve.

quotes.text: I voted Labour for years. But now I feel they take people like me for granted. I understand the concerns. I'm backing the Lib Dems this time.
Labour have abandoned their roots and you can't trust the Tories. I'm voting Lib Dems to deliver the real change we need.

images.caption: We're all backing Jo Shaw to deliver real change for us.
